### 3.2 Upload Product Image (Admin Only)
# การยิงแบบ multipart/form-data เพื่ออัปโหลดไฟล์จริงขึ้น Cloudinary
# ระบบจะส่งกลับ { url, publicId } เพื่อนำไปใช้ในขั้นตอนสร้างสินค้า
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="product-sample-1.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ../test-images/product-sample-1.png
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 4. Get Single Product (Detail with full specifications Map)
# เปลี่ยน ID หลังจากสร้างสินค้าสำเร็จ
@productId = 6a107359f476fc4f9eb9b739
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

### 5. Update Product - PUT (Replace/Full Update)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "brand": "Asus",
    "modelName": "ROG Zephyrus G16 - Updated",
    "price": 65900,
    "stock": 10,
    "category": "Notebook",
    "image": {
        "url": "https://res.cloudinary.com/jamine/image/upload/v12345/products/asus-g16-new.jpg",
        "publicId": "products/asus-g16-new"
    },
    "specifications": {
        "CPU": "Intel Core i9",
        "GPU": "RTX 4080",
        "RAM": "64GB"
    }
}

### 5.1 Partial Update - PATCH (Append/Modify Specifications, Stock, or Image)
# ทดสอบอัปเดตแบบเฉพาะเจาะจง
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "stock": 50,
    "specifications": {
        "Storage": "2TB NVMe",
        "Base Frequency": "3.5GHz"
    }
}

### 5.2 Error Case: Invalid Product ID Format
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/invalid-id-123

### 5.3 Error Case: Product Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/664b1d6f0000000000000000

### 6. Delete Product (Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

### 7. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/logout
